  "short_description": "CYMUT X MUTROBO is an action RPG, become a trainer of Cymut and Mutrobo and live the experience of farming, picking up items, exploring a huge world, completing quests, capturing and evolving up to 60 Cymuts and 60 Mutrobos to collect and use in battle.",
